262   // Optionally, we are shuffling the loaded vector element(s) into place.
263   // For the mask set everything but element 0 to undef to prevent poison from
264   // propagating from the extra loaded memory. This will also optionally
265   // shrink/grow the vector from the loaded size to the output size.
266   // We assume this operation has no cost in codegen if there was no offset.
267   // Note that we could use freeze to avoid poison problems, but then we might
